Decorator : Structural

- SDE at IceCream company
- build a s/w system which can build customise IceCreams

V1
= Class Explosion if we create classes for every Permutations & Combinations


V2
= All are ingredients - cone, scoops, choco chips

- << Ingredient >> double getCost(), string getDescription()
child classes = chocoCone, StrawCone, MangoScoop, ChocoChips

V3 final

<<Ingredient>> getCost(), getDescription
- ChocoCone, StrawCone, - Abstract Class IngredientDecorate { Ingredient baseIngredient }
Abstract Class IngredientDecorate { Ingredient baseIngredient }
add ons will inherit from this abstract class and in all of their constructors baseIngredient injected

